Nine months ago, the second floor of The Oval, Westlands, the home of tour company Moyo Holidays, bustled with activity as staff organised travel plans for international tourists. This frenzy of activity is still evident, except today, the office is the centre of operations of #TeamPankaj, an initiative that donates food relief to residents of Nairobi’s poorest slums.



